        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 7 at 6:04PM CDT until June 7 at 6:30PM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 604 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 7 miles north of
Persimmon Gap, or 30 miles north of Panther Junction, moving
southeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Golf ball size hail and 70 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect
considerable tree damage. Wind damage is also likely to
mobile homes, roofs, and outbuildings.

Locations impacted include...
Persimmon Gap.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
